title: Bobby’s Most Needed Country Collaboration List + Lunchbox Calls The News On Himself + 90’s TV Catchphrase Game!
itunes:title: Bobby’s Most Needed Country Collaboration List + Lunchbox Calls The News On Himself + 90’s TV Catchphrase Game!
description:
Bobby shares his list of the top seven collaborations needed in country music this year! Lunchbox called the news on himself as his alter ego “Niko Jackson” to give them a tip about his own good deed. Plus, we play the 90’s TV Catchphrase game where Bobby acts out the quote and the show members have to guess the show!
